Version 0.8.2 (May 11, 2021)
-------------------------------
* Added compatibilty with my AdvancedCardOptions-plugin, because they both OVERWRITE the same template-file (board/table_tasks.php)
* Added a ChangeLog

Version 0.8.1 (April 10, 2020)
-------------------------------
* Updated "version-tag" in Plugin.php

Version 0.8.0 (April 10, 2021)
-------------------------------
* Incorporated template-changes that came with Kanboard 1.2.12 > 1.2.18
* Added compatibilty with my DelegateTask-plugin, because both OVERWRITE the same template-file (board/table_column.php)
* Prepared compatibility with the upcoming new language "Deutsch (du)"

Version 0.7.0 (May 22, 2020)
-------------------------------
* Made adjustments for Kanboard 1.2.11
  * The new actions to reorder tasks by column (introduced with Kanboard 1.2.9) are ONLY displayed, if the current board is set to kanboard's default sort-method!
    * This also applies to the new possibility to sort columns by due date that came with Kanboard 1.2.11

Version 0.6.0 (May 22, 2020)
-------------------------------
* Made adjustments for Kanboard 1.2.9
  * The new actions to reorder tasks by column are ONLY displayed, if the current board is set to kanboard's default sort-method!

Version 0.5.0 (May 22, 2020)
-------------------------------
* initial release of the plugin developed with Kanboard Version 1.2.8
